The course content is free and open source, and hosted on GitHub. A link is available so that edits can be suggested via Pull Requests.
Suggesting Changes to The Course Material If you notice a typo or any other issues with the material, please open a pull request on GitHub by clicking the &ldquo;Edit this page&rdquo; button on the top right corner of every course page.
